{"tid":2180003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個餐廳發生嘅趣事","createTime":"2020-08-29T13:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:14:30.000Z","uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a28a658a8628dcffed620f7c0e8b9e058077264f","tid":2180003,"uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"小弟做侍應<br />\n喺一間放題餐廳返工<br />\n成日都會見到啲閪客<br />\n有一次有條女特別閪<br />\n好撚冇禮貌又係咁屌我啲同事<br />\n結果有個同事忍唔住<br />\n成塊鐵板車去佢頭上面<br />\n之後佢成身都係牛肉同牛肉汁<br />\n嬲到條女直接走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部同事 連經理都忍唔住讚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下有冇其他師兄有餐廳嘅趣事分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd01d2ad89d39e27806cfa6639b0dd878283e98","tid":2180003,"uid":260217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"善意的回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b5c71c3372a153b0e5c5a9e3f8e3a329bf33d9","tid":2180003,"uid":264299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"鐵板唔係熱㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定食剩嗰d"},{"pid":"12a4e05aaa0df5a0dbb2f957ffc658f2755ad13c","tid":2180003,"uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd01d2ad89d39e27806cfa6639b0dd878283e98","tid":2180003,"uid":260217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"善意的回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"尷尬死我 多謝清<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b9344970bf33b6c719579ca3252e3dfba431c7","tid":2180003,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd01d2ad89d39e27806cfa6639b0dd878283e98","tid":2180003,"uid":260217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"